
example:

./scotabc -b=ssd -c=4 -i /tmp/files_33.txt -s3-access-key=123456 -s3-endpoint=scontent-a.drom.ru -s3-secret-key=12341234 -max-proc 1

full option list

./scotabc 

~
~ СоЗФНЭСПГОРНСД 1.0
~ СалионоваОлегаЗагружающийФайлыНаЭс3ПосредствомГоРутинНаСервераДрома 1.0
~

One of this parameters is empty:
input file, access key, secret key, prefix, bucket name
-b="ssd1": bucket name
-c=20: concurency
-error-log="error.log": save errors to this file
-i="": input file
-max-proc=1: max proc count
-offset=0: count of lines to skip before start upload
-p="/var/www/": removes this string from key on PUT
-profile=false: save profiling to profile.prof on exit
-s3-access-key="": s3 access key
-s3-endpoint="scontent-a.drom.ru": s3 endpoint
-s3-secret-key="": s3 secret key
-silent=false: minimalizing logs
-use-http=false: use http instead https

